      "text": "（私達がグランプリ会場に入ると）\n（観客席は今日も満席だった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(When we enter the Grand Prix concert hall‚)\n(the audience is‚ once again‚ at full capacity.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.74233570098877,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
