      "text": "（三年ぶりのグランプリ開催は話題になり）\n（チケットもプレミア化しているらしかった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(The return of the Grand Prix after a three-year absence caused quite a buzz‚)\n(and tickets are apparently selling at a premium.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.042335700988769,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 16.809002367655435
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
