      "text": "（私達が案内されたのは、ステージを正面から）\n（見渡せる関係者席。みんなその景色に驚いていた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(We’re escorted into the concert hall from the guest seats‚)\n(which gives us a clear view of the stage. And everyone is startled by the view.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.24233570098876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 25.542335700988737
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_05-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "……明日、私達も\nこのステージで、歌うんですか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tomorrow… that’ll be us.\nWill we really be singing on that stage?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.50900236765543,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_05-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "そうなるわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yep. We really will.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.3756690343221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 31.37566903432213
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
