    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_05-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "観客が一人でも、十万人でも\nステージで歌うことには変わりはないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Doesn’t matter if it’s an audience of one or one hundred thousand.\nThat doesn’t change the fact that we’re singing on stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.15843549569448,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_05-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "そ……それは、そうかもしれない、けど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-that may be true‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.22510216236115,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 50.8926985025406
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
