      "text": "ええっ？\nさくらちゃん……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?\nSakura?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.65180014096773,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 55.60564622879028
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_05-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "そう思い込めば、楽しめるよ。今日の琴乃ちゃん達の\nステージも、明日の私達のステージも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Put yourself in that mindset‚ and you can enjoy yourself. We can enjoy Moon Tempest’s\nperformance today‚ and we can enjoy our own performance tomorrow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.64218842343584,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 63.001405811309795
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
