      "text": "へー\nねえ、武者震いって何？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ohh.\nDoesn’t that still mean you’re freaking out?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.84362808068592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "03-2d",
      "startTime": 93.37696141401925
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_05-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "それは…………\nそ、そのくらい自分で調べるのですわっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ um…\nH-how should I know!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.07696141401934,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "03-2d",
      "startTime": 98.27696141401934
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
